SHG Installation
****************

Prerequisites
-------------

Development environment is Linux debian 4.19.0-13-amd64 (Debian
Buster). Additionaly, GCC 10.2.0 or Clang 11.0.1, Boost C++ Libraries
1.75.0 and doxygen 1.9.0 are required for compilation and generating
documentation. To compile some inessential auxiliary programs, GNU
Multiple Precision Arithmetic Library and Numerical Recipes Third
Edition (version 3.02) are required.

Compilation and testing
-----------------------

Change directory to the main directory of the project. To build the
library, say make lib. To compile the testing program, say make
testing. To run the tests, say make check.

Documentation
-------------

To generate documentation, say make doc. The HTML documentation is
generated in doc/html directory.

Installation
------------

To install the library in /usr/local, say make install. To change the
installation directory, change the prefix variable near the top of
Makefile.
